Harry B. MALPUSS, Appellant, v. Joseph W. SANFORD, Warden, United States Penitentiary, Atlanta, Georgia, Appellee. No. 9337. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 13, 1940. No appearance was entered for appellant. Lawrence S.. Camp, U. S. Atty., and Harvey H. Tisinger and Jas. T. Manning, Asst. U. S. Attys., all of Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before SIBLEY, HUTCHESON, and McCORD, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
